The paper deals with interactive visualizations and data reduction techniques for large datasets, which are common topics in database systems (cs.DB) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The proposed method also involves optimization and approximation algorithms, which are relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and graphics (cs.GR).
